text: Walid Salah El-Din (Arabic وليد صلاح الدين) (born October 27, 1971) is an Egyptian footballer. Walid played as an attacking midfielder for Egyptian club side El-Ahly as well as the Egypt national football team. He played for Egypt at the 1999 FIFA Confederations Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian footballers Category:Egypt international footballers Category:1999 FIFA Confederations Cup players Category:Al Ahly SC players Category:Al Ittihad Alexandria Club players Category:Egyptian Premier League players Category:Association football midfielders
